item.description:
I am leading a 4 -5 mile off-leash hike down in Myles Standish State Forest. It will be at a moderate to brisk pace. We will meet at the Gate 30 parking lot. I drive a blue Jeep Cherokee. If you get misplace on your way there, please call my cell. (508) 559-3677

I am almost certain that the parking lot is on Upper College Pond Road, but please go on the Myles Standish Forest website and look at the map. I think it is Lot 2, but I am not positive.
item.name: Myles Standish State Forest
